<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">紀田產</cb:mulu>
<milestone unit="juan" n="7"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b10"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="7"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="7"><cb:jhead>雪峰志卷之七</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b11"/><byline cb:type="author">郡人　徐<g ref="#CB04521"/>　纂輯</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b12"/><byline cb:type="other">林弘衍　叅定</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b13"/><byline cb:type="other">鄭天綵　賴亨侯　吳興漢　重訂</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">紀生植</cb:mulu><head>紀生植</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b15"/><p xml:id="pB24p0617b1501" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">繄彼南中厥包橘柚入山既深厥土彌厚靈藥異
<lb ed="B" n="0617b16"/>花珍禽恠獸品物流形何嫌雜揉紀生植第七</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0617b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">穀</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0617b1701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">穀之屬　稉　秫　麥　麻　豆
<lb ed="B" n="0617b18"/>　蕎麥　<g ref="#CB23266"/></p></cb:div>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B24.0140.0618a" n="0618a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">木</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">木之屬　松　栢　檜　樟　黃楊
<lb ed="B" n="0618a02"/>　榕　桂　柟　楩　梓　椿
<lb ed="B" n="0618a03"/>　檉　棟　楓　杉　桐　桑
<lb ed="B" n="0618a04"/>　棕櫚　柳　橡<note place="inline">其子可食</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">竹</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618a0501" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">竹之屬　奯竹　麻竹　方竹　石竹　江南竹
<lb ed="B" n="0618a06"/>　觀音竹　紫竹　斑竹　綿竹　白箬竹</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">藥</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618a0701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">藥之屬　芝　黃精　茯苓　枸<g ref="#CB01096"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a08"/>　茱萸　紫蘇　香薷　天門冬　麥門冬
<lb ed="B" n="0618a09"/>　栝樓　使君子　石菖蒲　益母草　何首烏
<lb ed="B" n="0618a10"/>　車前子　茶　梔子</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">花</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">花之屬　風蘭<note place="inline">生於巖隙或寄生</note>　蕙　杜鵑花　萱草
<lb ed="B" n="0618a12"/>　茉莉　素馨　山丹　長春　海棠　闍提
<lb ed="B" n="0618a13"/>　石榴　百合　金燈　白長春　佛桑　葵
<lb ed="B" n="0618a14"/>　菊　木槿　雞冠　山茶　仙菊<note place="inline">一名西番蓮十月開
<lb ed="B" n="0618a15"/>　山中最多色絕紫</note>　金鳳　金錢　芙蓉　水仙
<lb ed="B" n="0618a16"/>　紫薇　<note n="0618a1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">刺【CB】，剌【補編】</note><app n="0618a1601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">刺</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">剌</rdg></app>牡丹<note place="inline">山中處處有之</note>　紫荊　玉釵　回頭顧子</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">蔬</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618a1701" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">蔬之屬　芥　菘　蘿蔔　萵苣　甕菜
<lb ed="B" n="0618a18"/>　菠稜　苦蕒　莙薘　茄　莧　蕨　薑
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B24.0140.0618b" n="0618b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b01"/>　冬瓜　匏　芹　芋　山藥　薯</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">果</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618b0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">果之屬　橄欖　柑　橘　柚　佛手柑
<lb ed="B" n="0618b03"/>　楊梅　枇杷　甘樜　芭蕉　棗　栗
<lb ed="B" n="0618b04"/>　瓜　柿　銀杏　石榴　梨　桃
<lb ed="B" n="0618b05"/>　李　黃彈　葡萄</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">鳥</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618b0601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">鳥之屬　白鷼　喜鵲　黃雀　鳩　黃鶯
<lb ed="B" n="0618b07"/>　燕　竹鷄　鷓鴣　雉　鴉　白頭公
<lb ed="B" n="0618b08"/>　鷹　啄木　鴝鵒　翠　杜鵑<note place="inline">閩中惟此山有之</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">獸</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB24p0618b0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">獸之屬　麂　鹿　麞　猴　兔　狸
<lb ed="B" n="0618b10"/>　竹<g ref="#CB06397"/>　穿山甲</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0618b11"/><p xml:id="pB24p0618b1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">論曰鳥獸草木隨地而產品類弗齊風氣殊也吾
<lb ed="B" n="0618b12"/>郡以西所產與東南稍異雪峰厥土高寒荔子輕
<lb ed="B" n="0618b13"/>紅地不宜植而琪葩瑤草瑞獸祥禽往往有之至
<lb ed="B" n="0618b14"/>若良材盤錯嘉穀豐登可資民生之日用者尤以
<lb ed="B" n="0618b15"/>是山為淵藪泉甘壤沃實稱奧區不徒佛地清凉
<lb ed="B" n="0618b16"/>但供緇流修習而<note n="0618b1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0618b1601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app></p></cb:div></cb:div>
